cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS

The paper proposes a reinforcement learning approach for exploring the policy space in Markov Decision Processes. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence and machine learning, which is covered by cs.AI. The paper also discusses the use of uncertainty and information theory, which are topics covered by cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The approach is evaluated on games, which suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of robotics (cs.RO) or systems and control (cs.SY).
